=== TEST 1: Counter Behavior Probe ===
Loading counters with motors OFF, checking if they count down.

T=0ms:  K2z= 1000  dZ=    0
T=50ms: K2z= 1000  dZ=    0
T=250ms: K2z= 1000  dZ=    0

Analysis:
  K2z: NOT counting (GATE likely controlled by motor enable)
  dZ: NOT counting (needs K2z output as clock, or GATE gated)

--- Sub-test: oscillator OFF ---
OSC OFF T=0:   K2z= 1000  dZ=    0
OSC OFF T=50ms: K2z= 1000  dZ=    0
  K2z: stopped when OSC off => OSC is the clock source

--- Sub-test: ZON=1, OSC OFF ---
ZON+OSCOFF T=0:   K2z= 1000  dZ= 5000
ZON+OSCOFF T=50ms: K2z= 1000  dZ= 5000
  K2z doesn't count => needs OSC

--- Sub-test: X axis (K2x, dX) for comparison ---
X: T=0: K2x=    0 dX=    0  T=50ms: K2x=14312 dX=    0

