=== TEST 3: 8254 Mode Detection (Read-Back) ===
Attempting Read-Back command on all counters.
(Works only on 8254-2. Original 8254 ignores this command.)

  PT0.ch0: status=0xE8  OUT=1  Mode=4  BCD=0
  PT0.ch1: status=0x00  OUT=0  Mode=0  BCD=0
  PT0.ch2: status=0xE8  OUT=1  Mode=4  BCD=0
  PT1.ch0: status=0xE8  OUT=1  Mode=4  BCD=0
  PT1.ch1: status=0x00  OUT=0  Mode=0  BCD=0
  PT1.ch2: status=0x88  OUT=1  Mode=4  BCD=0

Note: If all values look identical/random, chip may be 8254 (not 8254-2)
and Read-Back is not supported. Use TEST 1 behavioral results instead.

